    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i read online that if the infection is gone, the extra pills just mess up your gut health and can cause issues with your microbiome. since my skin is 100% clear now, isn't it actually better for my long-term health to just stop? it feels like a waste to keep taking medicine for a problem that isn't even there anymore.",
