      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i just feel like i'm being forced to take stuff for no reason. my doctor didnt even emphasize this much, just said take them for 10 days. if i stop now and it comes back, i'll just get more antibiotics then lol. it's way more efficient to just stop when the symptoms are gone, isn't it? like, why keep the dose going when the target is gone?",
